{"tid":645632,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"新手6月獨遊京阪神奈行程 求評 #adore#","createTime":"2018-04-28T10:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T21:02:13.000Z","uid":17667,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"56100612c036cf07971d5fc5ab720abca1b1698c","tid":645632,"uid":17667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我諗住6月一個人去京阪神奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩7日6夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前淨係去過東京，今次玩關西主要係想觀光同食野 唔會點行街shopping<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做左少少research 暫時plan左既行程係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay1 : 夜晚8點幾到機場，應該係機場食個晚飯就直去難波間酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay2: 海遊館、天保山摩天輪、浪花橫丁<br />\nDay3: USJ (我知道真係好毒，原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay4: 京都(半日伏見稻荷) + 嵐山(半日渡月橋/嵐山公園)<br />\nDay5: 奈良(東大寺、奈良公園) + 宇治 (平等院、中村) <br />\nDay6: 神戶(姬路城、北野)<br />\nDay 7: 黑門巿場、日本橋 fing到咁上下就去機場返歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我7日都會住難波，都好近地鐵站。想問咁plan會唔會太chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為清水寺維修緊，已經剔走左。姬路城同大阪城我都係二揀一。和服都放棄左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多地方我都係揀左最想去既就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832b6fc8cadc013d5242271d3caa4b022911f12f","tid":645632,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:27:56.000Z","msg":"你預計每日幾點起身先"},{"pid":"b939fb0ad6ab14d39a18fce889f719ccbe9412ea","tid":645632,"uid":17667,"like":2,"disl